<p>The following guidelines should be followed when writing content for Project27.</p>

<h2 id="1-length">1. Length</h2>

<p>The content on any single page should not exceed 18 minutes of estimated reading time.</p>

<h2 id="2-fres-readability-score">2. FRES readability score</h2>

<p>The <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fleschâ€“Kincaid_readability_tests">Flesch reading-ease score (FRES)</a>  should not be lower than 60.</p>
